data.description:
SELLER IS OFFERING A $5,000 CREDIT TOWARDS FLOORING!!! Welcome to your dream home in the beautiful B Section of Palm Coast, Florida! This immaculate residence, constructed by the renowned Adams Builders, boasts modern elegance and comfortable living, having been built in the last 5 years. Upon entering, you will be greeted by the inviting ambiance created by the high ceilings, providing a spacious and open feel throughout the home. The abundant natural light streaming through large windows enhances the bright and airy atmosphere, making every day feel like a vacation in the Sunshine State. The heart of this home lies in its stunning kitchen, which is a culinary enthusiast's delight. The kitchen's thoughtful design seamlessly flows into the dining area, creating the perfect setting for unforgettable gatherings and intimate family dinners.
The living spaces are designed with both relaxation and functionality in mind. The cozy living room invites you to unwind after a long day, and the designated office space offers an ideal environment for working from home or pursuing your hobbies and passions.
The home encompasses three generously sized bedrooms, each providing a peaceful retreat for restful nights. The master suite, in particular, exudes luxury, with its spacious layout, walk-in closet, and a private en-suite bathroom. The two additional bedrooms share a well-appointed second bathroom, making it convenient for family and guests.
As you step outside, you'll be delighted to discover a large, well-maintained backyard, providing endless possibilities for outdoor activities, from barbecues to gardening and playtime for kids and pets alike.
Located in the B Section of Palm Coast, you'll enjoy the convenience of nearby amenities, schools, parks, and recreational facilities. The area's pristine beaches and charming community atmosphere add to the allure of this delightful neighborhood.
Don't miss this opportunity to own a true gem in Palm Coast, Florida. Schedule a viewing today and envision your future in this impeccable Adams-built home with high ceilings, a fantastic kitchen, and a great-sized backyard - a perfect blend of modern comforts and coastal charm. Your ideal Florida lifestyle awaits!
